\c 3
\s Konke kulesikhathi sakho
\p
\v 1 Konke kulesikhathi esimisiweyo, njalo kulesikhathi\x + 3.17. 8.6.\x* sayo yonke indaba ngaphansi kwamazulu\x + 3.17. 5.4,8. 8.6. 12.1,10.\x*:
\v 2 Isikhathi sokuzalwa, lesikhathi sokufa\x + 3.20. Heb. 9.27.\x*; isikhathi sokuhlanyela, lesikhathi sokusiphuna okuhlanyelweyo\x + Zef. 2.4.\x*;
\v 3 isikhathi sokubulala, lesikhathi sokuphilisa; isikhathi sokudiliza, lesikhathi sokwakha;
\v 4 isikhathi sokukhala inyembezi, lesikhathi sokuhleka; isikhathi sokulila, lesikhathi sokugida\x + Neh. 8.9.\x*;
\v 5 isikhathi sokulahla amatshe, lesikhathi sokubuthelela amatshe\x + 2 Kho. 3.25.\x*; isikhathi sokugona, lesikhathi sokuba khatshana lokugona\x + Jow. 2.16. 1 Kor. 7.5.\x*;
\v 6 isikhathi sokudinga \add inzuzo\add*, lesikhathi sokuyekela kulahleke; isikhathi sokulondoloza, lesikhathi sokulahla;
\v 7 isikhathi sokudabula, lesikhathi sokuthunga\x + Gen. 44.13.\x*; isikhathi sokuthula, lesikhathi sokukhuluma\x + Amos 5.13.\x*;
\v 8 isikhathi sokuthanda, lesikhathi sokuzonda; isikhathi sempi, lesikhathi sokuthula.
\p
\v 9 Ulenzuzo bani osebenzayo kwatshikatshika kikho\x + 1.3. 2.22.\x*?
\v 10 Ngiwubonile umsebenzi\x + 1.13.\x* uNkulunkulu awunike abantwana babantu\x + Gen. 3.17-19.\x* ukuthi baphatheke ngawo\x + 1.13.\x*.
\v 11 Konke ukwenze kwaba kuhle\x + Gen. 1.31.\x* ngesikhathi sakho\x + Zaga 15.23.\x*; wasebeka iphakade enhliziyweni yabo\x + 9.1.\x*, ukuze kungabi lomuntu ongafumana umsebenzi uNkulunkulu awenzayo kusukela ekuqaleni kuze kube sekucineni\x + 8.17. Jobe 5.9.\x*.
\v 12 Ngiyazi ukuthi kakukho okuhle kubo ngaphandle kokuthokoza\x + 3.22.\x* lokwenza okuhle empilweni yakhe\x + Hlab. 34.14. 37.3.\x*.
\v 13 Futhi lokuthi wonke umuntu adle anathe\x + 2.24.\x* akholise okuhle ngomtshikatshika wakhe wonke\x + 2.1.\x*, kuyisipho sikaNkulunkulu\x + 5.19. 2.24. 9.9.\x*.
\v 14 Ngiyazi ukuthi konke uNkulunkulu akwenzayo kuzakuba khona phakade; kakukho okuzakwengezelelwa kukho, njalo kakukho okuzaphungulwa kukho; uNkulunkulu wakwenza ukuze besabe phambi kwakhe\x + Jak. 1.17.\x*.
\v 15 Lokho okwakukhona\x + 1.9.\x* kukhona khathesi\x + 1.10.\x*, lalokho okuzakuba khona sekuvele kukhona\x + 1.10.\x*; njalo uNkulunkulu ufuna okuxotshiweyo\x + 12.14.\x*.
\s Ukwahlulela lokulunga kakukho emhlabeni
\p
\v 16 Futhi ngasengibona ngaphansi kwelanga indawo yokwahlulela, kwakukhona ububi lapho; lendawo yokulunga, kwakukhona ububi lapho\x + 5.8. 4.1.\x*.
\v 17 Ngathi mina enhliziyweni yami: UNkulunkulu uzakwahlulela olungileyo lomubi\x + 12.14.\x*, ngoba kukhona lapho isikhathi\x + 3.1.\x* sayo yonke indaba lesawo wonke umsebenzi\x + Mat. 16.27.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Ngathi mina enhliziyweni yami ngesimo sabantwana babantu\x + 7.14. 8.2. Dan. 2.30.\x* ukuthi uNkulunkulu abatshengise obala\x + 9.1. Hez. 20.38. Dan. 11.35.\x* ukuthi babone ukuthi bona uqobo bazinyamazana\x + Hlab. 49.12,20. 73.22.\x*.
\v 19 Ngoba okwehlela abantwana babantu kwehlela lezinyamazana\x + 2.16.\x*; njalo yinye into ebehlelayo; njengoba omunye esifa, ngokunjalo enye iyafa; yebo konke kulomoya munye, lomuntu kalakho angadlula ngakho inyamazana; ngoba konke kuyize\x + 2.14.\x*.
\v 20 Konke kuya endaweninye; konke kuvela ethulini, njalo konke kubuyela ethulini\x + Gen. 3.19.\x*.
\v 21 Ngubani owazi umoya wabantwana babantu owenyukela phezulu, lomoya wenyamazana owehlela phansi emhlabathini\x + 12.7.\x*?
\v 22 Ngakho ngabona ukuthi kakukho okungcono okwedlula ukuthi umuntu azithokozise ngemisebenzi yakhe\x + 3.12. 2.24.\x*, ngoba lokhu kuyisabelo sakhe\x + 2.10.\x*. Ngoba ngubani ongamletha ukuthi abone lokho okuzakuba khona emva kwakhe\x + 6.12. 8.7. 10.14.\x*?